"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e也许是日有所思，昨晚做了个梦：一名十五岁天才少年证明了哥德巴赫猜想，在大会上无数人围绕着鼓掌，可惜梦到的少年是一个金头发的外国人，画面一转，来到了知乎这个问题的界面，所有回答全都删除了，只剩下一个关于大会视频的回答，醒来后我就想，或许在潜意识里这种事情只会发生在遥远的地方，而不是离我们近一些并在发知乎的人身上吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-586e0279d107ba429eabc8f970432dbb_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"690\" data-rawheight=\"690\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7ee6256035e223665cea749dcc0090fb_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"690\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-586e0279d107ba429eabc8f970432dbb_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='690'%20height='690'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"690\" data-rawheight=\"690\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7ee6256035e223665cea749dcc0090fb_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"690\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-586e0279d107ba429eabc8f970432dbb_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-586e0279d107ba429eabc8f970432dbb_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563057629,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"473f539757770e65e3fe41d55cb103a6","url_token":"you-xue-zhe-su-yi","name":"游学者Yui","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-fa76c433c62e3f43b9637cd16033af5f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-fa76c433c62e3f43b9637cd16033af5f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/473f539757770e65e3fe41d55cb103a6","user_type":"people","headline":"感觉不写就是强迫症还是写了比较厉害","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563057629","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546177496,"updated_time":1546177576,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e你说你证明了哥德巴赫猜想那你就证明了哥德巴赫猜想，你说你能上清华你就能上清华！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我朋友圈已经为你声援了！！！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e统一得到的回复是：还有27小时你说你（动物马）呢！！！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bb43d6bbcda908d29f94c3e0d4971180_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"102\" data-rawheight=\"97\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"102\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='102'%20height='97'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"102\" data-rawheight=\"97\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"102\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bb43d6bbcda908d29f94c3e0d4971180_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562766897,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a50fe96a11b62d185c0fcbb72ea1fb88","url_token":"mo-xiu-mo-xiu-mo-45","name":"是个狠人","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-f8d49c3bcd4023ec42328bc988035ddb_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-f8d49c3bcd4023ec42328bc988035ddb_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a50fe96a11b62d185c0fcbb72ea1fb88","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562766897","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546143785,"updated_time":1546143785,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e可以。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先，这是一个非常没有意思的假设。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果高中生可以证明哥德巴赫猜想，那他不仅可以被报送清北，他已经完全达到了清北博士毕业的水平。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e证明哥德巴赫猜想的过程可以出数篇甚至数十篇国际顶尖水平的论文，这些论文足够满足博士毕业的要求。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e依我所见，宝冠上的明珠之所以迷人不是在仅是定理有多么迷人，而更多的是在于证明的过程。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e几百年来人们为了证明费马定理开创了许多新的数学研究的方向。这些数学难题更像是一个引子，引导着人们不断的深入探索数学的世界。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还有，要想研究数学首先要能沉得住气。数学不像应用科学，研究数学几年甚至几十年没有进展是很常见的。如果你带着一颗功利的心去研究数学，那么这对你来说就是一场灾难。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=500\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=460\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2142}}
